summary: a total of 1282 proteins were identified from five age groups of worker bees. 43 (15.1%) of the DEPs were identified for the first time. the majority of these DEPs were up-regulated in the older workers. electronic supplementary material 12864_2014_6363_MOESM1_ESM.zip (2.2MB, zip) Additional file 1: Figure S1-S4: Figure S1, protein concentration and integrity. Figure S3, COG functional classification of the samples.
